<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>Premium — DeS Bot™</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rajdhani:wght@400;600;700&family=Orbitron:wght@700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{--gold:#D4AF37;--gold2:#FFD700;--bg:#070709;--bg2:#0D0D14;--text:#F0EDE8;--text2:#A89F8C;--text3:#6B6578;--border:rgba(212,175,55,0.15)}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;min-height:100vh}
body::after{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(212,175,55,.025) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(212,175,55,.025) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:50px 50px;pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 40px;height:70px;background:rgba(7,7,9,.9);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100}
.logo{font-family:'Orbitron',monospace;font-weight:900;font-size:1.4rem;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFD700,#D4AF37);-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;text-decoration:none}
.nav-links a{color:var(--text2);text-decoration:none;font-size:.9rem;margin-left:28px;transition:color .2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--gold)}
main{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 40px;position:relative;z-index:1;text-align:center}
.hero-badge{display:inline-block;background:rgba(212,175,55,.08);border:1px solid rgba(212,175,55,.25);padding:6px 16px;border-radius:100px;font-size:.8rem;color:var(--gold);font-family:'Rajdhani',sans-serif;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.1em;margin-bottom:24px}
h1{font-family:'Orbitron',monospace;font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3.5rem);font-weight:900;margin-bottom:16px}
h1 span{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold2),var(--gold));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}
.sub{color:var(--text2);font-size:1.05rem;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 60px;line-height:1.7}
.plans{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:24px;margin-bottom:80px}
.plan{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:20px;padding:40px 32px;transition:all .3s;position:relative;text-align:left}
.plan.featured{border-color:var(--gold);background:linear-gradient(160deg,var(--bg2),rgba(212,175,55,.06))}
.plan.featured::before{content:'BEST VALUE';position:absolute;top:-1px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold2),var(--gold));color:#0a0800;font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;padding:4px 14px;border-radius:0 0 10px 10px;font-family:'Rajdhani',sans-serif}
.plan-name{font-family:'Rajdhani',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:.9rem;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:10px}
.plan-price{font-family:'Orbitron',monospace;font-size:3rem;font-weight:900;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold2),var(--gold));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}
.plan-period{font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:28px}
.plan-features{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:13px;margin-bottom:36px}
.plan-features li{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;font-size:.9rem;color:var(--text2)}
.plan-features li span.check{color:var(--gold);font-size:.8rem;margin-top:2px;flex-shrink:0}
.plan-btn{display:block;text-align:center;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--gold2),var(--gold));color:#0a0800;font-weight:700;padding:14px;border-radius:10px;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Rajdhani',sans-serif;letter-spacing:.06em;font-size:1rem;transition:all .2s}
.plan-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(212,175,55,.4)}
.perks-title{font-family:'Orbitron',monospace;font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:900;margin-bottom:12px}
.perks-sub{color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:48px}
.perks-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(200px,1fr));gap:20px}
.perk{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:24px;text-align:left}
.perk-icon{font-size:1.8rem;margin-bottom:12px}
.perk-name{font-family:'Rajdhani',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;margin-bottom:6px}
.perk-desc{font-size:.85rem;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.6}
footer{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:36px 40px;text-align:center;color:var(--text3);font-size:.85rem;position:relative;z-index:1}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav>
  <a href="/" class="logo">DeS Bot™</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/">Home</a>
    <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
    <a href="https://discord.gg/dotesport">Support</a>
    <% if(user){ %><a href="/dashboard" style="color:var(--gold);font-weight:600">← Dashboard</a><% } else { %><a href="/auth/login" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FFD700,#D4AF37);color:#0a0800;font-weight:700;padding:8px 18px;border-radius:6px;margin-left:16px">Login</a><% } %>
  </div>
</nav>
<main>
  <div class="hero-badge">💎 PREMIUM PLANS</div>
  <h1>Unlock the <span>Full Power</span></h1>
  <p class="sub">Take your server to the next level with exclusive commands, boosted XP, and priority support.</p>

  <div class="plans">
    <div class="plan">
      <div class="plan-name">Basic</div>
      <div class="plan-price">$2.99</div>
      <div class="plan-period">per month / cancel anytime</div>
      <ul class="plan-features">
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 💎 Premium badge on profile</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 🎨 Custom embed color</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> ⚡ 1.5× XP boost</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 🪙 Daily coins ×1.5</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 📊 Advanced statistics</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 🎟️ Priority support</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://discord.gg/dotesport" class="plan-btn">Get Basic</a>
    </div>
    <div class="plan featured">
      <div class="plan-name">Pro</div>
      <div class="plan-price">$6.99</div>
      <div class="plan-period">per month / cancel anytime</div>
      <ul class="plan-features">
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> Everything in Basic</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 🚀 2× XP boost (24h activatable)</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 📝 Custom profile bio (200 chars)</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 🪙 Daily coins ×2</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 🏆 Tournament priority seeding</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 🎖️ Exclusive Pro badge</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> ⭐ Dedicated support queue</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://discord.gg/dotesport" class="plan-btn">Get Pro</a>
    </div>
    <div class="plan">
      <div class="plan-name">Elite</div>
      <div class="plan-price">$12.99</div>
      <div class="plan-period">per month / cancel anytime</div>
      <ul class="plan-features">
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> Everything in Pro</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 🔥 3× XP boost</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 👑 Exclusive Elite badge</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 🪙 Daily coins ×3</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 🔔 All future Premium features</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 💬 1-on-1 support channel</li>
        <li><span class="check">✦</span> 🗳️ Vote on new features</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://discord.gg/dotesport" class="plan-btn">Get Elite</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="perks-title">What You Get</div>
  <p class="perks-sub">Every premium tier includes these core benefits</p>
  <div class="perks-grid">
    <div class="perk"><div class="perk-icon">💎</div><div class="perk-name">Premium Badge</div><div class="perk-desc">Displayed on your profile, rank card, and leaderboard entries.</div></div>
    <div class="perk"><div class="perk-icon">🚀</div><div class="perk-name">XP Boost</div><div class="perk-desc">Level up faster with permanent multiplied XP per message.</div></div>
    <div class="perk"><div class="perk-icon">🪙</div><div class="perk-name">Bonus Coins</div><div class="perk-desc">More coins from daily and weekly rewards. Dominate the economy leaderboard.</div></div>
    <div class="perk"><div class="perk-icon">🎟️</div><div class="perk-name">Priority Support</div><div class="perk-desc">Your tickets get seen first. Dedicated support channels for Elite.</div></div>
    <div class="perk"><div class="perk-icon">🎨</div><div class="perk-name">Custom Color</div><div class="perk-desc">Set any hex color for your embeds. Stand out from the crowd.</div></div>
    <div class="perk"><div class="perk-icon">⚔️</div><div class="perk-name">Tournament Perks</div><div class="perk-desc">Priority seeding in tournaments. Exclusive premium-only events.</div></div>
  </div>
</main>
<footer>
  © 2024 DOT Esport · <a href="/" style="color:var(--gold);text-decoration:none">DeS Bot™</a> · All rights reserved
</footer>
</body>
</html>
